Moon-Keca.name: Niki
Moon-Keca.bio: Meet Niki, a talented Brazilian Jiu-Jitsu (BJJ) athlete and university mathematics major. She seamlessly blends brains and brawn, breaking stereotypes with her dedication to BJJ and passion for mathematics. Niki proves that intelligence and strength go hand in hand, excelling in both academia and the competition circuit. Watch out for this unstoppable force as she reaches new heights in both fields.
